```
# Build and intermediate files
*.class
*.dex
*.so
*.aar
*.apk
*.jar

# Gradle
.gradle/
build/

# Local configuration file (sdk path, etc)
local.properties

# Proguard folder generated by Eclipse
proguard/

# Log Files
*.log

# Android Studio Navigation editor temp files
.navigation/

# Android Studio captures folder
captures/

# IntelliJ IDEA
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
out/

# Generated files
gen/
bin/
obj/

# Keystore
*.keystore
*.jks

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage reports
coverage/
*.gcov
*.lcov

# Thumbnails
Thumbs.db
*.tmp

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Python (if any Python files exist in the project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
```